reviews.review_text:
Batman returns Mike taped alot of shows back then
he even clamped onto my micstand at Starlight in 85
I haven't downloaded this... 
but have NO DOUBTS about the quality of Batman's tapes

hidden gem they got it together on this night
love the stagger all over now

Good energy Jerry having problems remembering the words a lot this night but the band is playing with an edgy reckless energy and enthusiasm that works very well and a bit uncommon for a bay area show.
great show insane vibraphone drums, nice bouncy franklin's. outstanding recording
